# Galadriel execution rules

`AGENTS.md` is the primary repository instruction file.
Read it before you act.
Run its start commands before you change a file.
Read its required repository files.
Read each contract that owns the changed surface.

Read `RELEASE-POLICY.md` before release work.
Read `release/0.9.0/RELEASE-RUNBOOK.md` before qualification or publication.

Use the release runbook for every operator-only action.

